c: 2
v: 33
t: Allah Taalaa ney (hazrat) aadam (alh-e-salam) say farmaya tum inn kay naam bata do. Jab unhon ney bata diye to to farmaya kay kiya mein ney tumhen (pehlay hi) na kaha tha kay zamin aur aasmanon ka ghaib mein hi janta hun aur meray ilm mein hai jo tum zahir ker rahey ho aur jo tum chupatay thay